own-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="201">Yes, definitely upload the output as well. For this feature, the output screenshot demonstrates that the <strong data-start="105" data-end="134">random movement algorithm</strong> is actually running, which is valuable evidence in your portfolio.</p>
